          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "You're very welcome. I'm glad we could create a plan that addresses both your immediate medical needs and your need for reassurance. The combination of imaging to rule out anything concerning and targeted migraine treatment should give you both peace of mind and relief.\n\nPlease let me know how the triptan works for you and keep me updated about your symptoms. We'll review your CT scan results together and make sure you get the best possible care moving forward.\n\nTake care, and I hope you start feeling better soon."
