        },
        {
          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "You're very welcome, and I'm glad we could find a solution that works for you. It's important that we address both the physical symptoms and the emotional aspects of your care.\n\nTo summarize our plan:\n- CT scan arranged for today (you'll receive details about when and where)\n- Triptan nasal spray prescription ready for pickup\n- Monitor for any new or worsening symptoms\n- Follow up after results to discuss next steps\n\nYou've been very clear about your needs, and I appreciate you advocating for yourself. That CT scan will provide the reassurance you need, and the triptan should help with the immediate pain.\n\nTake care, and please don't hesitate to reach out if anything changes or you have any other concerns before our follow-up."
