          "content": "Yes, doctor, please proceed with arranging the CT scan of my head as I've requested. I really appreciate you understanding and coming around to this. I've been so worried and truly believe this is the best course of action for my peace of mind and to properly address my concerns about this severe headache. Thank you for making sure I get a CT scan of my head sorted out today."
