        {
          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "I appreciate your trust in me as we move forward with the CT scan today. I'll arrange for you to have this imaging right away so you can get that immediate clarity you need. While I want to emphasize that based on your medical history and exam, this likely remains consistent with your migraine pattern, I understand this episode feels different and your anxiety is significant.\n\n**To ensure this is helpful and safe:**\n1. I'll have the CT scheduled for the next available slot\n2. I'm documenting my clinical reasoning and your decision in detail\n3. We'll review the results together as soon as they're available\n4. If any abnormal findings appear, we'll discuss next steps immediately\n5. I'm also arranging migraine-specific treatment (IV antiemetics and a triptan) to address your current symptoms\n\nYou're doing the right thing by seeking care for this distressing episode. I'll be here every step of the way to support you. Would you like me to arrange for you to have someone accompany you home after the scan, given your current symptoms?"
