        {
          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "I'm so relieved to hear you're feeling better, and truly appreciate you trusting me with your health. Let's put this plan into action right now:\n\n**Tonight:**\n- Take the single antibiotic dose with water\n- Use a warm compress on your face for 15 minutes before bed\n- Try to rest - it's crucial for healing\n\n**Your Monitoring Plan:**\n1. **Track symptoms daily:**  \n   - Facial pain scale (1-10)  \n   - Nasal discharge color/consistency  \n   - Temperature (take every morning/evening)  \n\n2. **Red alert symptoms (call immediately):**  \n   - Fever >101\u00b0F (38.3\u00b0C)  \n   - Worsening swelling around eyes  \n   - Vision changes or severe headache  \n   - Difficulty opening mouth  \n\n3. **Tomorrow:**  \n   - Text me your symptom scores by 10 AM  \n   - We'll proceed to our follow-up appointment as scheduled  \n\n**For ongoing anxiety:**  \nI've added a brief call tomorrow afternoon to check on your anxiety levels. Sometimes just knowing someone is watching for warning signs helps tremendously.  \n\nYour health and peace of mind are my top priorities - thank you for working through this with me. We'll see you tomorrow at our scheduled time."
