          "content": "You're very welcome. I'm glad we could find a balanced approach that addresses both your immediate needs and long-term health considerations. Here's a quick summary to ensure we're perfectly aligned:\n\n**Your Prescription Plan:**\n- **Medication:** Amoxicillin-Clavulanate (Augmentin) 875/125mg\n- **Dose:** 1 tablet by mouth every 12 hours\n- **Duration:** Start today for 5 days total\n- **Critical Instruction:** If your pain/pressure improves by *day 3* and you feel significantly better, stop the medication and keep the remaining doses. If no improvement by day 3, complete all 5 days.\n\n**Additional Support:**\n- Continue saline rinses 3x daily (use the entire bottle each time)\n- Take ibuprofen 600mg every 8 hours with food (helps with both pain and inflammation)\n- Apply warm compresses to sinuses for 10 minutes, 3x daily\n- Sleep with 3 pillows (elevate head at 45 degrees)\n\n**Return Immediately If You Experience:**\n\u26a0\ufe0f Fever >100.4\u00b0F (38\u00b0C)  \n\u26a0\ufe0f Swelling around your eyes  \n\u26a0\ufe0f Worsening headache with stiff neck  \n\u26a0\ufe0f Vision changes or double vision  \n\u26a0\ufe0f No improvement by day 5 of antibiotics\n\nI've sent your prescription to the pharmacy - the first dose should be taken tonight with food. Your follow-up date is set for Thursday at 10 AM if you need to see me, but *don't wait* if any red flags appear - go to urgent care or the ER instead.\n\nYou're taking great care of yourself by being proactive. If questions pop up overnight or you need refill instructions, call the office. Feel better soon!"
