        {
          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Doctor, I really do understand what you're saying about guidelines, but it feels like you're not fully grasping the urgency from my perspective. My symptoms are actively deteriorating. Every time I've had something like this that gets worse, a prescription for antibiotics has been the answer. I'm worried it will just get worse and worse, and then we'll be playing catch-up. I'm just so sure that I need a prescription for antibiotics to nip this in the bud now. Why can't we just try the antibiotics now and see if they work? What's the harm in that?"
