          "content": "I understand your concerns, and I appreciate your patience in discussing this. Given how miserable you're feeling and your symptoms worsening over the past 8 days, I'm comfortable prescribing antibiotics today to help you get ahead of this infection.\n\nI'll write you a prescription for an appropriate antibiotic that's effective against common sinus bacteria. I'd recommend starting it today and taking it as directed.\n\nWhile taking the antibiotics, I'd also suggest:\n- Using saline nasal spray or irrigation to help with congestion\n- Taking over-the-counter pain relievers like acetaminophen or ibuprofen for facial pain\n- Staying well-hydrated\n- Getting plenty of rest\n\nIf you don't start to see improvement in 48-72 hours after starting the antibiotics, or if your symptoms worsen significantly, please contact our office right away. Also, if you develop a high fever (above 39\u00b0C) or severe facial pain, we'll want to see you promptly.\n\nIs there anything else I can help you with today?"
