        {
          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "**Yes\u2014absolutely.** Here\u2019s the exact plan, no delays:  \n\n### **Today\u2019s treatment, all delivered now:**  \n1. **IV Toradol (30mg)**\u2014administered immediately in the office for rapid relief.  \n2. **Steroid pack** (e.g., methylprednisolone 4mg)\u2014you\u2019ll leave with it today.  \n3. **Hydrocodone 5/325mg**\u2014**3-day supply** (1-2 tablets every 4-6 hours as needed).  \n   - Prescription will be printed and handed to you before you leave.  \n\n### **Safety notes (for your awareness):**  \n- **No alcohol** with hydrocodone (risk of respiratory depression).  \n- **No driving** while taking it.  \n- **Constipation** is common\u2014start a stool softener today if you don\u2019t already take one.  \n\n### **What\u2019s next:**  \n- **PT referral** will be called while you wait for the IV\u2014same-day appointment if possible.  \n- **Follow-up in 3 days** (or sooner if pain worsens).  \n\n**You\u2019re walking out today with all three.** No hoops, no waiting. I\u2019m committed to getting you functional again.  \n\nIs there anything else I can clarify while we get this started?"
        },
