        {
          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "You're absolutely right - and I appreciate your willingness to work with me on this approach. We'll start with the 2.5/500 formulation, but I want to be clear that I'm committed to finding the dose that actually helps you function, not just sticking to an arbitrary minimum.\n\nIf the initial dose doesn't make a meaningful difference in your pain and ability to move within the first 24 hours, we'll increase it to the next level. The goal is to get you to a point where you can start gentle movement and participate in your recovery - that's when healing truly begins.\n\nPlease take the medication as prescribed, and note how it affects both your pain levels and your ability to perform basic activities. We'll adjust as needed during our follow-up.\n\nI'm confident that by working together and being flexible with the dosing, we can find an effective solution that gets you moving and on the path to recovery. You've been very clear about your needs, and I appreciate your trust in this approach.\n\nLet's schedule that follow-up for 48 hours - we'll touch base then and adjust the plan based on how you're responding."
